quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Allah’s command has come, so dopl not rush it. Highly Exalted is He, and Most High above what they1 associate(with Him) ."
  16,2,"Hebestows1 the angels from on highwith the Spirit by His command upon whom He wills of His servants: “Givepl warning that there is no god but Me, so be mindful of Me.”"
  16,3,"He created the heavens and the earth with truth. Most High is He above what they associate(with Him) ."
  16,4,"He created man from a sperm-drop, yet he becomes an evident adversary!"
  16,5,"And livestock—He created them for youpl . In them are warmth and benefits for you, and of them you eat."
  16,6,"And there is beauty in them for you when you drive them home and when you drive them to pasture."